Firestarter/Unitron:


"Another time, pathetic Autobot.  There are things more important than you 
this day." Unitron said, transforming to space fighter mode, launching 
towards Firestarter, though moving to the side, almost knowing what 
Firestarter would do.

---

Firestarter smirked when Unitron moved out of his line of fire.  He raised an 
arm, a compartment in the bottom of his wrist extending downward, a missile 
visable.  The missile launched out down at Hot Rod's torso, as if to say 
"Don't mess with us, or else"
